"first_name": "Anne", "last_name": "Le H\u00e9nanff", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Didier", "last_name": "Lemaire", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Lise", "last_name": "Magnier", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Jean", "last_name": "Moulliere", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Na\u00efma", "last_name": "Moutchou", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "J\u00e9r\u00e9mie", "last_name": "Patrier-Leitus", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "B\u00e9atrice", "last_name": "Piron", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Christophe", "last_name": "Plassard", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Fran\u00e7ois", "last_name": "Portarrieu", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Marie-Agn\u00e8s", "last_name": "Poussier-Winsback", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Isabelle", "last_name": "Rauch", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Xavier", "last_name": "Roseren", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Laetitia", "last_name": "Saint-Paul", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Vincent", "last_name": "Thi\u00e9baut", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Valletoux", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}, {"first_name": "Anne-C\u00e9cile", "last_name": "Violland", "party": "Horizons & Ind\u00e9pendants"}], "summary": "Le pr\u00e9sent amendement vise \u00e0 pr\u00e9ciser les\u00a0domaines\u00a0sur lesquels les Etats-membres sont encourag\u00e9s \u00e0 intensifier leur surveillance. Il incite \u00e0 prendre en compte l'ensemble des moyens de contournement identifi\u00e9s dans un amendement propos\u00e9 plus haut, et doit donc \u00eatre consid\u00e9r\u00e9 en compl\u00e9ment de ce dernier.\nLa Russie a d\u00e9velopp\u00e9 des syst\u00e8mes alternatifs de paiement, notamment le SPFS (\u00e9quivalent russe de SWIFT) et des transactions en monnaies non occidentales, afin d\u2019\u00e9chapper aux sanctions financi\u00e8res. Elle\u00a0recourt \u00e0 des soci\u00e9t\u00e9s-\u00e9crans et \u00e0 des structures offshore afin de dissimuler l\u2019origine des fonds et de contourner les sanctions financi\u00e8res internationales. La Russie a \u00e9galement recours \u00e0 des transferts de cargaison en mer afin de masquer l\u2019origine de son p\u00e9trole et d\u2019\u00e9chapper aux sanctions internationales. Elle a enfin recourt \u00e0 une flotte de p\u00e9troliers dits \u00ab fant\u00f4mes \u00bb afin d\u2019exporter du p\u00e9trole en violation des sanctions internationales.\nL'identification pr\u00e9cise des diff\u00e9rentes strat\u00e9gies de contournement doit permettre d'\u00eatre plus efficace dans la mise en place de sanctions et leur suivi par les autorit\u00e9s fran\u00e7aises et europ\u00e9ennes."}